Summary: Contrail, popcorn on a string, 20 degree ark. easterly very high altitude.
trends: There have been 5 other sightings in Woodbridge
There were no other sightings in Woodbridge on or around July 17th 2010
divs: Sighting Detailsin the morning i observed a CONTRAIL of approx 20 degree in length in an easterly direction in Prince william county just west of Quantico. the beginning and the end of the contrail was very clear, and had a CLEAN central trail with perfect "popcorn" or donut necklace chains attached. i listened and could NOT pick up any taletale sounds . however i could also NOT pick up any regular airplane noise from any other jets at lower or same altitude. in ALL my sky wathing, and sightings of contrails i have NEVER seen such. i chanced the sighting while talking to a man on his porch at a higher angle, and was able to see it over his shoulder. it was morning, and the sky was clear except for other contrails. it took about 15 minutes for it to disperse.
